2006-11-05 15:37  alexpeshkoff

	* firebird2/: autogen.sh (1.8.2.2), configure.in (1.141.2.39),
	builds/make.new/config/config.h.in (1.1.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.boot.gpre (1.14.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.gbak (1.6.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.gdef (1.5.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.gfix (1.7.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.gpre (1.9.2.4),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.isql (1.6.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.qli (1.1.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.client.util (1.9.2.5),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.codes (1.7.2.2),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.gbak (1.6.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.gdef (1.5.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.gfix (1.7.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.gpre (1.9.2.4),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.isql (1.6.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.lockmgr (1.5.2.2),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.qli (1.10.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.embed.util (1.8.2.4),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.extern.editline (1.2.2.2),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.extlib (1.10.2.8),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.fbserver (1.11.2.7),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.fbutil (1.6.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.gpre (1.8.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.inet_server (1.11.2.4),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.intl (1.11.2.5),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.libfbclient (1.14.2.6),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.libfbcommon (1.6.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.libfbembed (1.10.2.5),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.libfbserver (1.6.2.5),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.libfbstatic (1.5.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.msgs (1.12.2.1),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.static.gbak (1.6.2.2),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.static.gpre (1.10.2.3),
	builds/posix/Makefile.in.static.isql (1.6.2.1),
	builds/posix/make.defaults (1.25.2.10), builds/posix/make.rules
	(1.19.2.3), builds/posix/make.shared.targets (1.13.2.2),
	builds/posix/prefix.aix (1.1.2.1):

	Ported firebird 1.5 to AIX. Main required changes: 1. Force use of
	xlC compiler in AIX case.  2. Changed ALIGNMENT to be FB_ALIGNMENT
	to avoid conflicts with AIX .h files.  3. Changed jrd/thread and
	dsql/var strcutures' names for same reason.  4. Now it's possible
	to set extension of dependency files.  5. Now it's possible to set
	LIB_LINK in prefix.OS file.  6. Fix for #define isc_facility in
	codes.epp.  7. Added AIX specific threading (they have pthreads
	slightly different from linux).  8. And - a lot of (IPTR) were
	needed.  There are also some small fixes, where xlC wanted, but
	they are trivial enough not to mention here.

