2004-10-22 00:26  arnobrinkman

	* firebird2/doc/WhatsNew (1.36.2.29):

	Hopefully this comment is clear enough :-/

	Example by code, with what i meant :

	SELECT * FROM	TableX x   LEFT JOIN TableY y ON (y.FK = x.PK)
	WHERE	x.FieldX IN (1,2,3,4,5)

	and "x.FieldX" isn't included in a index

