	deleted as part of make clean

2003-12-13 13:16  dimitr

	* firebird2/builds/win32/msvc6/: Firebird2.dsw (1.19.2.4),
	common.dsp (1.21.2.1), common_classic.dsp (1.15.2.1), engine.dsp
